               <p>JOSEPH SIMPSON. I am the prisoner's father. I bought this coat on Monday, and told him to after the buttons; he is a tailor, and works at home. I put it into my drawer, and next day it was gone.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18270531-156-person925">
